  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to observe and explore the effect of single or combined&#xD;
      treatment of arotinib on the survival and prognosis of patients with advanced esophageal&#xD;
      cancer in the real world, and to summarize the treatment experience of a wide range of&#xD;
      people.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
